    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gelatin that is chemically purer and physically more refined than food-quality gelatin and is used as the binding medium in some photographic emulsions.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
